comments: Gasol (TOR) sets the pick in Nunn's (MIA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Siakam (TOR) and Adebayo (MIA) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Siakam (TOR) briefly grasps Adebayo's (TOR) arm, but the contact does not affect his FOM.
Winslow (MIA) is not in a legal guarding position when contact occurs with Lowry's (TOR) arm that affects his ability to gather the ball.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Lowry (TOR) off ball in the post.
Lowry (TOR) initiates contact with Winslow's (MIA) arm during his drive and affects his SQBR.

There is no conclusive angle that shows if Powell's (TOR) foot is out of bounds when he receives the pass.  After the Replay Center communicated with the courtside administrator, the ruling on the floor of a 3pt field goal by Powell stands.
Gasol (TOR) sets the screen in Winslow's (MIA) path and absorbs the contact when contact occurs.
VanVleet (TOR) briefly engages with Nunn (MIA) before separating.

Replay review of the foul called on Gasol (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Gasol turns his body and initiates body contact with Butler (MIA) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) is inside of the three-point arc before Butler (MIA) releases his free throw attempt.
Siakam (TOR) initiates marginal contact with Jones Jr. (MIA) before Jones Jr. cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Adebayo (MIA) sets the screen in Powell's (TOR) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Powell (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
